{"type":"message","id":"4f5c82f8","parentId":"3853d8fb","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:16:10.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我已经获得了四个领域的搜索结果，让我整理出3-5条对道简网络有价值的商业信息。每条信息包含：标题+核心内容+价值点。\n\n让我从四个领域的信息中筛选出最有价值的：\n\n1. **企业数字化转型政策/补贴**：\n   - 中央数字化转型专项（第三批）：补贴最高2000万元，最低15%，最高30%上浮\n  ","thinkingSignature":""}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":5559,"output":0,"cacheRead":30641,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36200,"cost":{"input":0.0016676999999999998,"output":0,"cacheRead":0.0009192299999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00258693}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1773944167298,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted."}}
